web.feedback.help_us_improve.translation: Āwhinatia mātou ki te whakapai ake

web.feedback.help_content_goes_here.translation: Ka noho te ihirangi āwhina ki konei.

web.feedback.thanks_for_helping_onetime_.en: Thanks for helping Onetime Secret improve. It means a lot.
web.feedback.thanks_for_helping_onetime_.translation: Ngā mihi mō tō āwhina ki a Onetime Secret ki te whakapai ake. He mea nui tēnei.

web.feedback.weve_built_this_tool_to_hel.en: We've built this tool to help you share sensitive info securely, and your real-world experiences are crucial for focusing our efforts. It helps us figure out what to work on next and how to make the service better for everyone.
web.feedback.weve_built_this_tool_to_hel.translation: Kua hangaia e mātou tēnei taputapu hei āwhina i a koe ki te tuari mōhiohio tairongo i runga i te haumaru, ā, he mea nui ō wheako ao-tūturu mō te arotahi i ā mātou mahi. Ka āwhina i a mātou ki te whakatau he aha te mahi ā muri ake nei me te pēhea te whakapai ake i te ratonga mō te katoa.

web.feedback.hey_there_thanks_for_stoppi.en: Hey there, thanks for stopping by our feedback page. Your input isn't just welcome - it's crucial.
web.feedback.hey_there_thanks_for_stoppi.translation: Tēnā koe, ngā mihi mō tō toro mai ki tā mātou whārangi urupare. Ehara tō kōrero i te mea pōwhiri noa - he mea nui.

web.feedback.a_note_from_delano_founder_.en: A note from Delano, founder of Onetime Secret
web.feedback.a_note_from_delano_founder_.translation: He tuhipoka mai i a Delano, kaiwhakarewa o Onetime Secret
